Right-click on the Taskbar, select &quot;New Toolbar&quot; and then select a folder
or drive. Then drag the re-size handle until it is just a chevron.
Clicking on that chevron will expand the menu.  You can add any folder or
drive, and the list will automagically update if the target folder or
drive contents change (instructions for Windows 2000, but should work
for XP).
